|WKBClan: Commands
|WKO--------------

|YKOAvailable to the entire MUD:
|YKBcwar <#>          |BKB-- |GKBLook at information from wars that have already ended.
|YKBcwar list            |GKBThe information accessed via this command is deleted
                     over time. Older wars vanish after awhile, etc.
|YKBclans             |BKB-- |GKBList the available clans on Darkwind.
|YKBclaninfo <clan>   |BKB-- |GKBRead information about a particular clan.
|YKBwho <clan>        |BKB-- |GKBSee who is logged on from a particular clan.
|YKBwclan             |BKB-- |GKBShow all clan members logged on, sorted by clan reputation.
|YKBwclan leader      |BKB-- |GKBShow all clan leaders logged on, sorted by clan reputation.


|YKOAvailable to anyone in a clan:
|YKBcl/ecl <msg>      |BKB-- |GKBTalk/emote on your clan channel.
|YKBclhist            |BKB-- |GKBDisplay clan channel history.
|YKBclwho             |BKB-- |GKBSee who is logged in from your clan.
|YKBcstat             |BKB-- |GKBSee statistics about your clan.
|YKBclleave           |BKB-- |GKBLeave your clan.
|YKBclemote           |BKB-- |GKBClan emote. Works on channels like normal emotes.
                     Leaders can talk to James to have the emote customized 
                     for their clan.
|YKBcvote             |BKB-- |GKBVote on outstanding clan issue (listed in cstat).
|YKBcheckclan         |BKB-- |GKBCheck if you have unread message on your clan board.


|YKOAvailable to clan members while in the Clan Operations Room:
|YKBcdeposit <coins>  |BKB-- |GKBDeposit money into clan coffers.
|YKBcwithdraw <coins> |BKB-- |GKBWithdraw money from clan coffers.
|YKBcbalance          |BKB-- |GKBShow the number of coins currently in the coffers.


|YKOAvailable to clan leaders:
|YKBleadercmds        |BKB-- |GKBList all your leader-only commands.
|YKBcinitiate         |BKB-- |GKBAdd someone to your clan.
|YKBcdismiss          |BKB-- |GKBDismiss someone from your clan.
|YKBcdeclare          |BKB-- |GKBAsk a clan leader if he/she wants to start a war.
|YKBchangedesc       |BKB -- |GKBChange description of a room in clan headquarters.
                     Can only be used while in one of the rooms.
|YKBcdescribe         |BKB-- |GKBChange the information shown in 'claninfo'
|YKBcaddissue         |BKB-- |GKBAdd issue for members to vote on.
|YKBcdelissue         |BKB-- |GKBRemove outstanding issue, preventing additional votes.
|YKBctithe            |BKB-- |GKBSet your clan automatic tithe amount.

|YKOPlease see |YKB"help clans" |YKOfor a basic overview.
|YKOPlease see |YKB"help clans basics" |YKOfor a more detailed intro to clans.
|YKOPlease see |YKB"help clans war" |YKOfor warfare information.
